rows.label: tlk70000035_04_msg0001
rows.name:
Have you ever thought about doing
a performance with us?

rows.label: tlk70000035_04_msg0002
rows.name:
With Invidians, Gulans, Iirans, and
Blades all in the mix, don't you think
we could come up with a great tune?

rows.label: tlk70000035_04_msg0003
rows.name:
Well, maybe it's not such a good idea.
It'd tank our business if you ended up
being more popular than us.

rows.label: tlk70000035_04_msg0004
rows.name:
And you definitely would be! After all,
you're already famous...
